===Adjective===
{{en-adj|salti|er}}

# Tasting of [[salt]].
# Containing [[salt]].
# Coarse, provocative, earthy; said of language.
# Experienced, especially used to indicate a veteran of the naval services.
# {{linguistics}} Pertaining to those dialects of [[Catalan]], spoken in the [[Balearic]] Islands and along the coast of [[Catalonia]], that use definitive articles descended from the Latin {{term|lang=la|ipse||self}} instead of the Latin {{term|lang=la|ille||that}}.

